          0,
          "It‚Äôs not just one person's role to do community engagement - it‚Äôs everybody‚Äôs role. You need to adapt the culture around that idea, not just think about technology. How do you activate your community as citizens? What‚Äôs the public value in what you‚Äôre doing beyond the transaction?"
